Ask HN: Suggestions for academic/research journals discussing AI-generated art?
text:
I'm a first year engineering student, and for my technical writing class we need to write an informative paper. I chose AI art and it's influence on our society as my topic.
One of the criteria is to have at least 5 academic/research journals in your references. I'm having difficulty with this because AI art is such a new topic. Does anyone know some academic/ research journals that they're willing to share? Even if the article is just about generative algorithms in general that's a great help. Thank you in advance.
